text: Leïla Maknoun (born 19 January 1992, Paris, France), is a French-Tunisian female footballer who plays as a forward for FF Issy in Division 1 Féminine of France. ==Club career== Played for Paris FC, Saint-Maur B, Blanc-Mesnil and then PSG U19, PSG B and the first team of PSG.
